queries.compiledQueryString:
select 
    ticker,
    calendar_date,
    dayname(calendar_date) as day,
    calendar_date - (EXTRACT(DOW FROM calendar_date) + 6) % 7 AS reporting_week,
    d1${inputs.start_metric.value}${inputs.end_metric.value}_pos_100d as metric
from strk.last_200d 
where ticker = lower('${params.ticker}')
